BOE’s Posen Says Europe Will Resolve Crisis, Euro Will Be ‘Fine’

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-09-27T09:31:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/boe-s-posen-says-europe-will-resolve-crisis-euro-will-be-fine-.html
Bank of England  policy maker  Adam
Posen  said  Europe  will resolve its debt crisis and the euro will
survive.  “I do believe the crisis will be resolved, I do belive the
euro will be fine,” Posen said at an event in Berlin today. “I
don’t mind if you quote me on that,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
